<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-08-0276 </DOCNO><TEXT>This report details findings and recommendations relating to certain activitiesin the Engineering Prototype Group at the Rockwell Rocky Flats Plant(Rockwell). The purpose of the audit was to determine if administrativeinternal controls had been established to deter a recurrence of reportedunauthorized activities; to evaluate Rockwell's current policy for makingmedallions and using precious metals; and to identify the cost incurredon reported improprieties, and the extent to which those costs are recoverable.</TEXT></DOC>